NAME
	retire
 
SYNOPSYS
	retire from coding
 
DESCRIPTION
	With the command "retire from coding", any wizard in the rank of
	domain wizard till Liege can retire him or herself. This will take
	away the coding powers (even from mages), make you leave the domain
	you have been working in and automatically demotes you to the rank
	of "retired wizard".
 
WARNING
	There is no instant undo if you change your mind. Retired wizards
	may later request from the administation to be set back to the rank
	of apprentice in order to apply to a domain again.
